sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant User as Person
  participant RFID as RFID/NFC Reader
  participant HS as Hardware Service
  participant Redis as Redis Pub/Sub
  participant ACS as Access Control Service
  participant CS as Chip Service
  participant Door as Door Relay/Lock
  participant UI as Dashboard

  User->>RFID: Present chip
  RFID->>HS: UID read
  HS->>Redis: Publish hardware.events (rfid.scan)
  Redis-->>ACS: Deliver rfid.scan event
  ACS->>CS: POST /chips/validate {uid}
  CS-->>ACS: {chip_id, enabled, balance}
  alt Enabled and balance >= fee
    ACS->>CS: POST /chips/{id}/balance/adjust {-fee}
    CS-->>ACS: {new_balance}
    ACS->>HS: POST /door/open {seconds}
    HS->>Door: Toggle relay (unlock)
    HS-->>ACS: 204
    ACS->>Redis: Publish access.events (granted)
    Redis-->>UI: WS event stream (granted)
  else Denied
    ACS->>Redis: Publish access.events (denied + reason)
    Redis-->>UI: WS event stream (denied)
  end

